snippet.title: Tenebris Somnia by Andrés Borghi - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Demo trailer of TENEBRIS SOMNIA, the 8-bit Survival Horror with Live Action Cutscenes developed by Andrés Borghi and Tobías Rusjan, published by Saibot Studios. Play the demo on Steam!
http://tenebrissomnia.com/

Follow the project on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/TenebrisSomnia

And Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/tenebrissomnia_game/
